text: Yanic Gentry or Yanic Arno Gentry Torfer (born 20 February 1991) is a Mexican sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics, in the Laser class, and placed 42nd among 46 participants. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican sailors Category:Olympic sailors of Mexico Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser Category:Sailors at the 2015 Pan American Games
